{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects/task-21","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects/task-21"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Da li Brian predlaže prebacivanje/promenu iz marketinga putem društvenih mreža u e-mail marketing?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Da, predlaže e-mail marketinški pristup kao alternativu marketingu preko društvenih mreža.</p>","feedback":"<p>Brian koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">also</span> u svojoj izjavi, što ukazuje na to da je dodavanje, a ne menjanje.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ne, predlaže ga kao dodatnu strategiju paralelno sa marketingom na društvenim mrežama.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Da, zato što e-mail marketing je ekonomičniji od marketinga na društvenim mrežama.</p>","feedback":"<p>Ekonomičnost nije osnova za izabravanje alternative; Brian dodaje, a ne menja, strategiju društvenih mreža.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ne, jer misli da prodaja društvenih mreža nije uspešna</p>","feedback":"<p>Predlog Braiana ne znači da misli da je prodaja društvenih mreža neuspešna; umesto toga, predlaže dodatnu strategiju.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"living-room.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0},{"character":"Brian","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"8.2-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":5.92,"finishTimestamp":20.66},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.36,"dialogue":{"text":"I think we're going to focus on social media marketing.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.84,"finishTime":6.76,"dialogue":{"text":"It's cost-effective and it will reach a broader audience.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":7.11,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":"company1-boardroom.png","character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":7.11,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.46,"finishTime":11.4,"dialogue":{"text":"That sounds good. I suggest that we also invest in email marketing.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.54,"finishTime":15.74,"dialogue":{"text":"It's more targeted and it will allow us to engage with our subscribers directly.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":16.24,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 21","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","dashedName":"task-21","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","isFirstStep":false,"templa